## Start

The authoritative process lives in `docs/process/`. If this repository has
just been initialized, start with `docs/process/start-here.md` and guide the
user through Greenfield or Brownfield as a dialogue. For normal work, read the
product frame `PRODUCT.md` — the direction every change is checked against.

